Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才所做的不过是模仿空破斩罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
