Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜就…拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:19:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 蕾娜
